---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Contact HHZ"
  description="Contact points for editorial inquiries, corrections, press, methodology questions, and the grievance officer at HHZ Respiratory Review."
>
  <article class="prose">
    <h1>Contact HHZ</h1>

    <p class="lead">
      Use the addresses below to reach the right desk. Each inbox is monitored by the team
      that owns that workflow, which means a correction doesn't land with the writer whose
      work is in question, and a press enquiry doesn't get buried in the editorial queue.
    </p>

    <h2>Editorial inquiries</h2>
    <p>
      Story pitches, reader questions you'd like us to cover, feedback on an article, or
      anything else that does not fit one of the specialised desks below.
    </p>
    <p><a href="mailto:editor@homehealthzone.com">editor@homehealthzone.com</a></p>

    <h2>Corrections</h2>
    <p>
      If you've spotted a factual error — a wrong spec, an outdated price, a mis-cited
      clinical claim — this is the fastest way to get it fixed. Please include the article
      URL, a direct quote of the incorrect passage, and a verifiable source for the correct
      information. See our full <a href="/correction-policy/">correction policy</a>.
    </p>
    <p><a href="mailto:corrections@homehealthzone.com">corrections@homehealthzone.com</a></p>

    <h2>Press and media</h2>
    <p>
      Interview requests, commentary for your publication, and permission queries for
      republishing excerpts.
    </p>
    <p><a href="mailto:press@homehealthzone.com">press@homehealthzone.com</a></p>

    <h2>Methodology questions</h2>
    <p>
      Questions about how a particular measurement was taken, what equipment we used, or how
      our scoring rubric is weighted. Researchers and clinical reviewers reach out here most
      often.
    </p>
    <p><a href="mailto:methodology@homehealthzone.com">methodology@homehealthzone.com</a></p>

    <h2>Grievance officer (India IT Rules 2021)</h2>
    <p>
      For grievances relating to data handling, content you believe has been published in
      violation of the Intermediary Guidelines, or takedown requests backed by a legal basis.
      Acknowledged within 24 hours, resolved within 15 days as the Rules require.
    </p>
    <address>
      Grievance Officer, HHZ Respiratory Review<br />
      <a href="mailto:grievance@homehealthzone.com">grievance@homehealthzone.com</a>
    </address>

    <h2>Send us a note</h2>
    <p>
      The form below opens your email client pre-filled. If your client doesn't open, email
      us directly at one of the addresses above.
    </p>

    <form action="mailto:editor@homehealthzone.com" method="post" enctype="text/plain" class="contact-form">
      <p>
        <label for="name">Your name</label><br />
        <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required />
      </p>
      <p>
        <label for="email">Your email</label><br />
        <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required />
      </p>
      <p>
        <label for="subject">Subject</label><br />
        <input type="text" id="subject" name="subject" required />
      </p>
      <p>
        <label for="message">Message</label><br />
        <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="6" required></textarea>
      </p>
      <p>
        <button type="submit">Send</button>
      </p>
    </form>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
